    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a definitive 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, benefitting from a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite including rod bearing replacement and a Beisan VANOS overhaul. The high-revving power unit is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally pristine, with a reinforced rear subframe ensuring long-term rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint depth is exceptional, complemented by an interior devoid of typical bolster wear or pixel degradation. The suspension kinematics remain sharp, utilizing OEM components to preserve the original M-division damping profile. This is a mechanically transparent, collector-quality vehicle with a complete service dossier.",
      "price": 48500.0,
